              <h2><a name="Become_a_Member" id="Become_a_Member"></a>Become a Member</h2>
              		<div class="content-left">
                    	While anyone can play Club Penguin for free, members have access to special features in Club Penguin. To find out more about a Club Penguin membership visit our <a href="https://secure.clubpenguin.com/membership/" >Membership page</a>. 
                    </div>
                    <div class="content-right">
                    	<img src="images/become-member.gif" width="350" height="220" />
                    </div>
		<div align="right"><a href="#top" >back to top</a><a href="#top"></a>        </div>
        
        
        
		<h2><a name="Edit_Account" id="Edit_Account"></a>Edit Your Account</h2>
        		<div class="content-left">
                	<p>To change your password, chat mode or cancel your membership while you are logged in to Club Penguin, click the <img src="images/edit-player-icon.gif" width="20" height="20" /> icon on your player card menu. To cancel your monthly membership, the account username and password are required. </p>
                    <p>To change the chat mode, check the box at the bottom of the Edit Your Account screen.To learn more about each chat mode, go to <a  href="communicating.htm">Communicating.</a></p>
                </div>
                <div class="content-right">
                	<img src="images/cancel-membership.gif" width="350" height="220" />
                </div>  
